	(390022, 5161729, 121361, 10, 'The Story So Far (2015)', 0, 12, '2015-03-16', 'Ahead of the eagerly-anticipated fifth season, we bring you up tp speed with the events of the epic fantasy drama to date. \r\n\r\nAnd to help the uninitiated ease into the wild world of Westeros, here\'s a beginner\'s guide to the fantasy epic.', '', 1503211061),
